      <example name="take advantage of" src="">
        <text>Sales climbed 71 % to $ 6.36 billion from $ 3.72 billion as the company capitalized on the ravenous global demand for commercial airliners .</text>
        <propbank>
          <rel relloc="15">capitalized</rel>
          <arg type="ARG0" start="13" end="14">the company</arg>
          <arg type="ARG1" start="16" end="23">on the ravenous global demand for commercial airliners</arg>
